release.notes: Fixed some security hole and changed base language from Japanese to English on the pc_frontend.
Added an ability to render iframes of the outer OpenSocial container and fixed the PersistentAPI.

Fix some bug and fix unit test
Fixed API bug and change screen translation about invite.
